data.title: Ike Turner, Tina’s Ex-Husband and Music Partner, Dies at 76
data.meta_description: Ike Turner, the R&B musician, songwriter, bandleader, producer and talent scout who discovered Tina Turner, died yesterday at his home in California. He was 76. Here's Tina and Ike performing "Proud Mary" during their glory days. They never did anything nice and easy.
